Updates
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The most current version will govern our processing of your personal data and will always be available on our website. This Privacy Policy is subject to periodical review to always comply with applicable regulations and to reflect new functionalities of our services. Your continued use of our services confirms your acceptance of our updated Privacy Policy.
Terms and Conditions
